361        if ($this->getPresentation()->getPresentationProperties()->isLoopContinuouslyUntilEsc()) {
362            $objWriter->writeAttribute('presentation:endless', 'true');
363            $objWriter->writeAttribute('presentation:pause', 'PT0S');
364            $objWriter->writeAttribute('presentation:mouse-visible', 'false');
365        }
366        if ($this->getPresentation()->getPresentationProperties()->getSlideshowType() === PresentationProperties::SLIDESHOW_TYPE_BROWSE) {
367            $objWriter->writeAttribute('presentation:full-screen', 'false');
368        }
369        $objWriter->endElement();
370
371        // > office:presentation
372        $objWriter->endElement();
373        // > office:body
374        $objWriter->endElement();
375        // > office:document-content
376        $objWriter->endElement();
377
378        // Return
379        return $objWriter->getData();
380    }

474    /**
475     * Write text.
476     */
477    protected function writeShapeTxt(XMLWriter $objWriter, RichText $shape): void
478    {
479        // draw:frame
480        $objWriter->startElement('draw:frame');
481        $objWriter->writeAttribute('draw:style-name', 'gr' . $this->shapeId);
482        $objWriter->writeAttribute('svg:width', Text::numberFormat(CommonDrawing::pixelsToCentimeters((int) $shape->getWidth()), 3) . 'cm');
483        $objWriter->writeAttribute('svg:height', Text::numberFormat(CommonDrawing::pixelsToCentimeters((int) $shape->getHeight()), 3) . 'cm');
484        $objWriter->writeAttribute('svg:x', Text::numberFormat(CommonDrawing::pixelsToCentimeters((int) $shape->getOffsetX()), 3) . 'cm');
485        $objWriter->writeAttribute('svg:y', Text::numberFormat(CommonDrawing::pixelsToCentimeters((int) $shape->getOffsetY()), 3) . 'cm');
486        // draw:text-box
487        $objWriter->startElement('draw:text-box');
488
489        $paragraphs = $shape->getParagraphs();
490        $paragraphId = 0;
491        $sCstShpLastBullet = '';
492        $iCstShpLastBulletLvl = 0;
493        $bCstShpHasBullet = false;
494
495        foreach ($paragraphs as $paragraph) {
496            // Close the bullet list
497            if ('bullet' != $sCstShpLastBullet && true === $bCstShpHasBullet) {
498                for ($iInc = $iCstShpLastBulletLvl; $iInc >= 0; --$iInc) {
499                    // text:list-item
500                    $objWriter->endElement();
501                    // text:list
502                    $objWriter->endElement();
503                }
504            }
505            //===============================================
506            // Paragraph
507            //===============================================
508            if ('none' == $paragraph->getBulletStyle()->getBulletType()) {
509                ++$paragraphId;
510                // text:p
511                $objWriter->startElement('text:p');
512                $objWriter->writeAttribute('text:style-name', 'P_' . $paragraph->getHashCode());
513
514                // Loop trough rich text elements
515                $richtexts = $paragraph->getRichTextElements();
516                $richtextId = 0;
517                foreach ($richtexts as $richtext) {
518                    ++$richtextId;
519                    if ($richtext instanceof TextElement) {
520                        // text:span
521                        $objWriter->startElement('text:span');
522                        if ($richtext instanceof Run) {
523                            $objWriter->writeAttribute('text:style-name', 'T_' . $richtext->getHashCode());
524                        }
525                        if (true === $richtext->hasHyperlink() && '' != $richtext->getHyperlink()->getUrl()) {
526                            // text:a
527                            $objWriter->startElement('text:a');
528                            $objWriter->writeAttribute('xlink:type', 'simple');
529                            $objWriter->writeAttribute('xlink:href', $richtext->getHyperlink()->getUrl());
530                            $objWriter->text($richtext->getText());
531                            $objWriter->endElement();
532                        } else {
533                            $objWriter->text($richtext->getText());
534                        }
535                        $objWriter->endElement();
536                    } elseif ($richtext instanceof BreakElement) {
537                        // text:span
538                        $objWriter->startElement('text:span');
539                        // text:line-break
540                        $objWriter->startElement('text:line-break');
541                        $objWriter->endElement();
542                        $objWriter->endElement();
543                    }
544                }
545                $objWriter->endElement();
546            //===============================================
547            // Bullet list
548            //===============================================
549            } elseif ('bullet' == $paragraph->getBulletStyle()->getBulletType()) {
550                $bCstShpHasBullet = true;
551                // Open the bullet list
552                if ('bullet' != $sCstShpLastBullet || ($sCstShpLastBullet == $paragraph->getBulletStyle()->getBulletType() && $iCstShpLastBulletLvl < $paragraph->getAlignment()->getLevel())) {
553                    // text:list
554                    $objWriter->startElement('text:list');
555                    $objWriter->writeAttribute('text:style-name', 'L_' . $paragraph->getBulletStyle()->getHashCode());
556                }
557                if ('bullet' == $sCstShpLastBullet) {
558                    if ($iCstShpLastBulletLvl == $paragraph->getAlignment()->getLevel()) {
559                        // text:list-item
560                        $objWriter->endElement();
561                    } elseif ($iCstShpLastBulletLvl > $paragraph->getAlignment()->getLevel()) {
562                        // text:list-item
563                        $objWriter->endElement();
564                        // text:list
565                        $objWriter->endElement();
566                        // text:list-item
567                        $objWriter->endElement();
568                    }
569                }
570
571                // text:list-item
572                $objWriter->startElement('text:list-item');
573                ++$paragraphId;
574                // text:p
575                $objWriter->startElement('text:p');
576                $objWriter->writeAttribute('text:style-name', 'P_' . $paragraph->getHashCode());
577
578                // Loop trough rich text elements
579                $richtexts = $paragraph->getRichTextElements();
580                $richtextId = 0;
581                foreach ($richtexts as $richtext) {
582                    ++$richtextId;
583                    if ($richtext instanceof TextElement) {
584                        // text:span
585                        $objWriter->startElement('text:span');
586                        if ($richtext instanceof Run) {
587                            $objWriter->writeAttribute('text:style-name', 'T_' . $richtext->getHashCode());
588                        }
589                        if (true === $richtext->hasHyperlink() && '' != $richtext->getHyperlink()->getUrl()) {
590                            // text:a
591                            $objWriter->startElement('text:a');
592                            $objWriter->writeAttribute('xlink:type', 'simple');
593                            $objWriter->writeAttribute('xlink:href', $richtext->getHyperlink()->getUrl());
594                            $objWriter->text($richtext->getText());
595                            $objWriter->endElement();
596                        } else {
597                            $objWriter->text($richtext->getText());
598                        }
599                        $objWriter->endElement();
600                    } elseif ($richtext instanceof BreakElement) {
601                        // text:span
602                        $objWriter->startElement('text:span');
603                        // text:line-break
604                        $objWriter->startElement('text:line-break');
605                        $objWriter->endElement();
606                        $objWriter->endElement();
607                    }
608                }
609                $objWriter->endElement();
610            }
611            $sCstShpLastBullet = $paragraph->getBulletStyle()->getBulletType();
612            $iCstShpLastBulletLvl = $paragraph->getAlignment()->getLevel();
613        }
614
615        // Close the bullet list
616        if ('bullet' == $sCstShpLastBullet && true === $bCstShpHasBullet) {
617            for ($iInc = $iCstShpLastBulletLvl; $iInc >= 0; --$iInc) {
618                // text:list-item
619                $objWriter->endElement();
620                // text:list
621                $objWriter->endElement();
622            }
623        }
624
625        // > draw:text-box
626        $objWriter->endElement();
627        // > draw:frame
628        $objWriter->endElement();
629    }

670    /**
671     * Write table Shape.
672     */
673    protected function writeShapeTable(XMLWriter $objWriter, Table $shape): void
674    {
675        // draw:frame
676        $objWriter->startElement('draw:frame');
677        $objWriter->writeAttribute('svg:x', Text::numberFormat(CommonDrawing::pixelsToCentimeters((int) $shape->getOffsetX()), 3) . 'cm');
678        $objWriter->writeAttribute('svg:y', Text::numberFormat(CommonDrawing::pixelsToCentimeters((int) $shape->getOffsetY()), 3) . 'cm');
679        $objWriter->writeAttribute('svg:height', Text::numberFormat(CommonDrawing::pixelsToCentimeters((int) $shape->getHeight()), 3) . 'cm');
680        $objWriter->writeAttribute('svg:width', Text::numberFormat(CommonDrawing::pixelsToCentimeters((int) $shape->getWidth()), 3) . 'cm');
681
682        $arrayRows = $shape->getRows();
683        if (!empty($arrayRows)) {
684            $firstRow = reset($arrayRows);
685            $arrayCells = $firstRow->getCells();
686            // table:table
687            $objWriter->startElement('table:table');
688            foreach ($arrayCells as $shapeCell) {
689                $objWriter->startElement('table:table-column');
690                $objWriter->endElement();
691            }
692            foreach ($arrayRows as $keyRow => $shapeRow) {
693                // table:table-row
694                $objWriter->startElement('table:table-row');
695                $objWriter->writeAttribute('table:style-name', 'gr' . $this->shapeId . 'r' . $keyRow);
696                //@todo getFill
697
698                $numColspan = 0;
699                foreach ($shapeRow->getCells() as $keyCell => $shapeCell) {
700                    if (0 == $numColspan) {
701                        // table:table-cell
702                        $objWriter->startElement('table:table-cell');
703                        $objWriter->writeAttribute('table:style-name', 'gr' . $this->shapeId . 'r' . $keyRow . 'c' . $keyCell);
704                        if ($shapeCell->getColspan() > 1) {
705                            $objWriter->writeAttribute('table:number-columns-spanned', $shapeCell->getColspan());
706                            $numColspan = $shapeCell->getColspan() - 1;
707                        }
708
709                        // text:p
710                        $objWriter->startElement('text:p');
711
712                        // text:span
713                        foreach ($shapeCell->getParagraphs() as $shapeParagraph) {
714                            foreach ($shapeParagraph->getRichTextElements() as $shapeRichText) {
715                                if ($shapeRichText instanceof TextElement) {
716                                    // text:span
717                                    $objWriter->startElement('text:span');
718                                    if ($shapeRichText instanceof Run) {
719                                        $objWriter->writeAttribute('text:style-name', 'T_' . $shapeRichText->getHashCode());
720                                    }
721                                    if (true === $shapeRichText->hasHyperlink() && '' !== $shapeRichText->getHyperlink()->getUrl()) {
722                                        // text:a
723                                        $objWriter->startElement('text:a');
724                                        $objWriter->writeAttribute('xlink:type', 'simple');
725                                        $objWriter->writeAttribute('xlink:href', $shapeRichText->getHyperlink()->getUrl());
726                                        $objWriter->text($shapeRichText->getText());
727                                        $objWriter->endElement();
728                                    } else {
729                                        $objWriter->text($shapeRichText->getText());
730                                    }
731                                    $objWriter->endElement();
732                                } elseif ($shapeRichText instanceof BreakElement) {
733                                    // text:span
734                                    $objWriter->startElement('text:span');
735                                    // text:line-break
736                                    $objWriter->startElement('text:line-break');
737                                    $objWriter->endElement();
738                                    $objWriter->endElement();
739                                }
740                            }
741                        }
742
743                        // > text:p
744                        $objWriter->endElement();
745
746                        // > table:table-cell
747                        $objWriter->endElement();
748                    } else {
749                        // table:covered-table-cell
750                        $objWriter->writeElement('table:covered-table-cell');
751                        --$numColspan;
752                    }
753                }
754                // > table:table-row
755                $objWriter->endElement();
756            }
757            // > table:table
758            $objWriter->endElement();
759        }
760        // > draw:frame
761        $objWriter->endElement();
762    }

793    /**
794     * Writes a group of shapes.
795     */
796    protected function writeShapeGroup(XMLWriter $objWriter, Group $group): void
797    {
798        // draw:g
799        $objWriter->startElement('draw:g');
800
801        $shapes = $group->getShapeCollection();
802        foreach ($shapes as $shape) {
803            // Increment $this->shapeId
804            ++$this->shapeId;
805
806            // Check type
807            if ($shape instanceof RichText) {
808                $this->writeShapeTxt($objWriter, $shape);
809            } elseif ($shape instanceof Table) {
810                $this->writeShapeTable($objWriter, $shape);
811            } elseif ($shape instanceof Line) {
812                $this->writeShapeLine($objWriter, $shape);
813            } elseif ($shape instanceof Chart) {
814                $this->writeShapeChart($objWriter, $shape);
815            } elseif ($shape instanceof AbstractDrawingAdapter) {
816                $this->writeShapeDrawing($objWriter, $shape);
817            } elseif ($shape instanceof Group) {
818                $this->writeShapeGroup($objWriter, $shape);
819            }
820        }
821
822        $objWriter->endElement(); // draw:g
823    }

851    /**
852     * Write the default style information for a RichText shape.
853     */
854    protected function writeTxtStyle(XMLWriter $objWriter, RichText $shape): void
855    {
856        // style:style
857        $objWriter->startElement('style:style');
858        $objWriter->writeAttribute('style:name', 'gr' . $this->shapeId);
859        $objWriter->writeAttribute('style:family', 'graphic');
860        $objWriter->writeAttribute('style:parent-style-name', 'standard');
861        // style:graphic-properties
862        $objWriter->startElement('style:graphic-properties');
863        $objWriter->writeAttribute('style:mirror', 'none');
864        $this->writeStylePartShadow($objWriter, $shape->getShadow());
865        if (is_bool($shape->hasAutoShrinkVertical())) {
866            $objWriter->writeAttribute('draw:auto-grow-height', var_export($shape->hasAutoShrinkVertical(), true));
867        }
868        if (is_bool($shape->hasAutoShrinkHorizontal())) {
869            $objWriter->writeAttribute('draw:auto-grow-width', var_export($shape->hasAutoShrinkHorizontal(), true));
870        }
871        // Fill
872        switch ($shape->getFill()->getFillType()) {
873            case Fill::FILL_GRADIENT_LINEAR:
874            case Fill::FILL_GRADIENT_PATH:
875                $objWriter->writeAttribute('draw:fill', 'gradient');
876                $objWriter->writeAttribute('draw:fill-gradient-name', 'gradient_' . $shape->getFill()->getHashCode());
877                break;
878            case Fill::FILL_SOLID:
879                $objWriter->writeAttribute('draw:fill', 'solid');
880                $objWriter->writeAttribute('draw:fill-color', '#' . $shape->getFill()->getStartColor()->getRGB());
881                break;
882            case Fill::FILL_NONE:
883            default:
884                $objWriter->writeAttribute('draw:fill', 'none');
885                $objWriter->writeAttribute('draw:fill-color', '#' . $shape->getFill()->getStartColor()->getRGB());
886                break;
887        }
888        // Border
889        if (Border::LINE_NONE == $shape->getBorder()->getLineStyle()) {
890            $objWriter->writeAttribute('draw:stroke', 'none');
891        } else {
892            $objWriter->writeAttribute('svg:stroke-color', '#' . $shape->getBorder()->getColor()->getRGB());
893            $objWriter->writeAttribute('svg:stroke-width', number_format(CommonDrawing::pointsToCentimeters($shape->getBorder()->getLineWidth()), 3, '.', '') . 'cm');
894            switch ($shape->getBorder()->getDashStyle()) {
895                case Border::DASH_SOLID:
896                    $objWriter->writeAttribute('draw:stroke', 'solid');
897                    break;
898                case Border::DASH_DASH:
899                case Border::DASH_DASHDOT:
900                case Border::DASH_DOT:
901                case Border::DASH_LARGEDASH:
902                case Border::DASH_LARGEDASHDOT:
903                case Border::DASH_LARGEDASHDOTDOT:
904                case Border::DASH_SYSDASH:
905                case Border::DASH_SYSDASHDOT:
906                case Border::DASH_SYSDASHDOTDOT:
907                case Border::DASH_SYSDOT:
908                    $objWriter->writeAttribute('draw:stroke', 'dash');
909                    $objWriter->writeAttribute('draw:stroke-dash', 'strokeDash_' . $shape->getBorder()->getDashStyle());
910                    break;
911                default:
912                    $objWriter->writeAttribute('draw:stroke', 'none');
913                    break;
914            }
915        }
916
917        $objWriter->writeAttribute('fo:wrap-option', 'wrap');
918        // > style:graphic-properties
919        $objWriter->endElement();
920        // > style:style
921        $objWriter->endElement();
922
923        $paragraphs = $shape->getParagraphs();
924        $paragraphId = 0;
925        foreach ($paragraphs as $paragraph) {
926            ++$paragraphId;
927
928            // Style des paragraphes
929            if (!isset($this->arrStyleParagraph[$paragraph->getHashCode()])) {
930                $this->arrStyleParagraph[$paragraph->getHashCode()] = $paragraph;
931            }
932
933            // Style des listes
934            $bulletStyleHashCode = $paragraph->getBulletStyle()->getHashCode();
935            if (!isset($this->arrStyleBullet[$bulletStyleHashCode])) {
936                $this->arrStyleBullet[$bulletStyleHashCode]['oStyle'] = $paragraph->getBulletStyle();
937                $this->arrStyleBullet[$bulletStyleHashCode]['level'] = '';
938            }
939            if (false === strpos($this->arrStyleBullet[$bulletStyleHashCode]['level'], ';' . $paragraph->getAlignment()->getLevel())) {
940                $this->arrStyleBullet[$bulletStyleHashCode]['level'] .= ';' . $paragraph->getAlignment()->getLevel();
941                $this->arrStyleBullet[$bulletStyleHashCode]['oAlign_' . $paragraph->getAlignment()->getLevel()] = $paragraph->getAlignment();
942            }
943
944            $richtexts = $paragraph->getRichTextElements();
945            $richtextId = 0;
946            foreach ($richtexts as $richtext) {
947                ++$richtextId;
948                // Not a line break
949                if ($richtext instanceof Run) {
950                    // Style des font text
951                    if (!isset($this->arrStyleTextFont[$richtext->getHashCode()])) {
952                        $this->arrStyleTextFont[$richtext->getHashCode()] = $richtext;
953                    }
954                }
955            }
956        }
957    }
